information: Bio Can Marti is the biggest organic farm in Barcelona area of quality shell eggs. Source of brown and white eggs, our procedures comply with the organic regulations and certifications. Production capacity of 1 million layers per month. All types of packaging available and Incoterm negotiable- ExW, FOB, CIF, etc. We have our logistics and sanitary regulations service, ready to export our products worldwide. We also produce organic broth (vegetable, chicken an beef) and organic meat of chicken and turkey. Short term and long term contract.
products: Organic fresh eggs | Organic vegetable broth | Organic Chicken /beef broth
